On Wed, 12 Mar 2003, Markus Benne wrote:

> So I assembled everything with my gf doublechecking everything I did, and we
> took a 150km drive.
> After the drive I jacked up the car pushed and pulled on the wheel, and although
> I thought at first I could feel some play, after a couple tugs I couldn't.

You should be able to feel a bit of play when pulling the bottom of the
wheel out and pushing the top in.  If you're not feeling _any_ I'd be
suspicious that things are too tight.  Check it!

